athletes.Name: Michael Milstead
athletes.Biography: My name is Michael Milstead, I play golf at East Texas Baptist University. I have a year and a half of eligibility left. I am a former football player at Texas A&M university and Coty College of San Francisco. My story is like a roller coaster and I am certain that my testimony will move others. I play and live for the Glory of God and want to challenge the critics who don’t believe in me. I dealt with some much adversity, much self inflicted, but have dedicated my life to betterment and to change the narrative. I am ready to become the man I was destined to be all along.
